  "title": "Temperature Screener",
  "description": "<p>Are you willing to be part of a healthcare team and play a rewarding role in contributing to public health and safety?</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>About The Role</strong></p><p>As a Temperature Screener at the Airport, your scope of work includes:</p><ul><li>Perform Temperature Screening duties of passengers at designated locations in Changi Airport</li><li>Regulate the movement of the passengers at the duty stations to ensure temperature is successfully taken</li><li>Identify and approach febrile individuals politely and tactfully</li><li>Assist in ushering passengers to health stations when required</li><li>Assist in any other duties as assigned by Duty Managers/Supervisors.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Pleasant personality with customer service skills</li><li>Fit and healthy, good mobility and able to stand during work hours</li><li>Able to start work immediately </li><li>All are welcome to apply</li><li>Training is provided</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Working Location</strong></p><ul><li>Airport Terminals</li><li>Various shifts of 4, 6 or 12 hours</li><li>Morning or night shifts available</li><li>Must be Singaporean to exchange NRIC for airport pass</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Who We Are</strong><br /><br />PeopleSolve is an international search firm recruiting experienced and qualified nurses from around the world. Our program is specifically designed to help Singapore & internationally educated nurses succeed permanently in our strategic partner’s healthcare organizations in Singapore and beyond.<br /><br />Since our beginning in 2021, we have helped 6,000 + nurses and healthcare professionals, both full time and part time, to secure placements in key healthcare locations including hospitals, clinics, community care centers, testing and vaccination centers.<br /><br />At PeopleSolve, we specialize in recruitment and outsourcing solutions for the healthcare industry.</p><p><br />Cyrus Thong</p><p>Registration No.: R24122254</p><p>PeopleSolve Pte Ltd</p><p>EA Licence No.: 21C0695</p>",
